. Treasuries are Treasuries; =E2=80=9Cmost investment mandates and regulato=
ry regimes refer to them specifically, rather than AAA-rated government deb=
t.=E2=80=9D But AAA-rated quasi-government-supported asset-backed-securitie=
s are, maybe, in some contexts, just AAA bonds. Or=C2=A0rather they were, a=
nd=C2=A0now they are not.

